;;   ...................................................
;;   (even, even, odd ) |   bb#   | >
;;   ...................................................
;;   (even, odd,  even) |   b#b   | ,
;;   ...................................................
;;   (odd,  even, even) |   #bb   | [
;;   ...................................................
;;   (even, odd,  odd ) |   b##   | ]
;;   ...................................................
;;   (odd,  even, odd ) |   #b#   | .
;;   ...................................................
;;   (odd,  odd,  even) |   ##b   | <
;;   ...................................................
;;   (odd,  odd,  odd ) |   bbb   | -
